 to run the GUI with normal docker you must

 build :

   docker build -t et .

run:

   docker run --rm   --gpus all   -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY   -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix   et

if your on linux you must configure 

xhost +local:docker

i dont use windows or mac so i dont know if it will run out of the gate, 

to compile shaders use 

chmod +x compile.sh

./compile.sh
